{"tid":432330,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"IVE 太陽能車隊成港唯一代表出戰世界太陽能車挑戰賽","createTime":"2017-10-11T12:08:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-18T02:12:55.000Z","uid":14170,"like":76,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"14f99d98964339ede71e5970047122e9e542c989","tid":432330,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T12:08:13.000Z","msg":"賽事由 8 Oct 至 15 Oct 舉行，IVE 砌左架真太陽能車係賽道奔馳，同各國出戰大學能隊伍一決高下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n暫時排名 4th<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/10/163307_b8c4adb777ca850cca6e2677e9b3ae47.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F10%2F163307_b8c4adb777ca850cca6e2677e9b3ae47.jpg&h=8a10d210&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由 17 位追到上 4 位，未來三日將會係追上首名既關鍵時刻，請各位香港人同我地一齊支持香港代表 IVE Solar Car team <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSophie IV 介紹<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/10/163744_d2c03217ae4ce568e71d701dbe7245e6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F10%2F163744_d2c03217ae4ce568e71d701dbe7245e6.jpg&h=79c3fa7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.worldsolarchallenge.org/team/view/105-ive-solar-car-team\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldsolarchallenge.org%2Fteam%2Fview%2F105-ive-solar-car-team&d=ToG9cpkj6Vi99OCoKNxottU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=f7d5a167\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.worldsolarchallenge.org/team/view/105-ive-solar-car-team</a><br />\n<br />\n賽道介紹<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/10/163859_0538c3205c9f10750ed76dc157835150.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F10%2F163859_0538c3205c9f10750ed76dc157835150.jpg&h=9b163c47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.worldsolarchallenge.org/event-information/route_map\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldsolarchallenge.org%2Fevent-information%2Froute_map&d=ToG9cpkj6Vi99OCoKNxottU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=9998c570\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.worldsolarchallenge.org/event-information/route_map</a><br />\n<br />\n參賽隊伍不乏世界級名校，最出名既大學包括 劍橋大學 史丹福大學 密西根大學 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nIVE 有機會代表香港同呢啲世界級名校較量，可以話係香港之光 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"784277686f0e1395b9cb71d578cc9d4a6dbb9b39","tid":432330,"uid":14170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T12:08:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/10/183731_71580ff9695af9aea3e6ae3219fdac6c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F10%2F183731_71580ff9695af9aea3e6ae3219fdac6c.jpg&h=cde29170&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢架來自新加坡理工學院既 Sunspec5 外型真係睇到流哂口水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"435821720e9223ddf76f2696d6803a7f009f94b0","tid":432330,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T12:09:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/10/184106_bbc158e4d81e7094e1d00765739978ed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F10%2F184106_bbc158e4d81e7094e1d00765739978ed.jpg&h=68ec10fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嘩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好想揸下</blockquote>"},{"pid":"f2b75e63dd39463e4b908d468779d0c7020f8d72","tid":432330,"uid":13467,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T12:11:43.000Z","msg":